      {
        "name": "My name is Conundrum!",
        "species": "Dog",
        "breed": "Bichon Frise",
        "age": "Unknown",
        "gender": "Unknown",
        "bio": "Believe me honey, I was just as surprised as you to learn that an adorable and happy guy like ME could end up at the shelter as a stray. But I'm livin', breathin' proof that life takes you the places you least expect and when it does, there are good things waiting for you. They call me Conundrum and I'm hoping to call you mine. I'm social, friendly, affectionate, adorable, gentle...the list of good qualities goes on and on. I'm just waiting for someone like YOU to scoop me up and make my life the best it has ever been. See you soon?",
        "photo": null,
        "url": "https://www.adoptapet.com/pet/47375212-wausau-wisconsin-bichon-frise-mix"
      },
      {
        "name": "My name is Honey!",
        "species": "Dog",
        "breed": "Mixed Breed (Medium)",
        "age": "Unknown",
        "gender": "Unknown",
        "bio": "I heard ya'll were looking to grow your family by four paws and I'm hoping to be the lucky dog you choose. I'm a high energy girlie who is playful, curious and downright adorable. I'm social with other dogs but will need my food, treats and high value items kept separate. I'm looking for an active lifestyle with adventure around every corner and in return I'll love you like no dog ever has. Wanna shake on it?",
